column1: DEV_ENTERPRISE_LANDING."insurance"."protection_plan" pp INNER JOIN DEV_ENTERPRISE_LANDING."insurance"."insurance_policy" ip on pp."policy_id" = ip."id" INNER JOIN DEV_ENTERPRISE_LANDING."insurance"."insurance_provider" ipr on ip."insurance_provider_id" = ipr."id"
DEV_ENTERPRISE_LANDING."insurance"."protection_plan_status" pps INNER JOIN DEV_ENTERPRISE_LANDING."insurance"."protection_plan_status_log" ppsl ON pps."protection_plan_status_log_id" = ppsl."id"
DEV_ENTERPRISE_LANDING."jaglms"."collection_lms_loan_map" clm INNER JOIN DEV_ENTERPRISE_LANDING."jaglms"."collections" c on c."collection_id" = clm."collection_id"

DEV_ENTERPRISE_LANDING."jaglms"."lms_payment_schedules" ps INNER JOIN DEV_ENTERPRISE_LANDING."jaglms"."lms_base_loans" bl ON ps."base_loan_id" = bl."base_loan_id" INNER JOIN DEV_ENTERPRISE_LANDING."jaglms"."lms_customer_info_flat" ci ON bl."customer_id" = ci."customer_id" INNER JOIN DEV_ENTERPRISE_LANDING."jaglms"."lms_payment_schedule_items" psi ON ps."payment_schedule_id" = psi."payment_schedule_id"
DEV_ENTERPRISE_LANDING."jaglms"."lms_customer_info_flat" c inner join DEV_ENTERPRISE_LANDING."jaglms"."upm_organizations" uo on c."organization_id" = uo."organization_id"
DEV_ENTERPRISE_LANDING."jaglms"."lms_base_loans" bl inner join DEV_ENTERPRISE_LANDING."jaglms"."lms_loan_header" lh on bl."loan_header_id" =  lh."loan_header_id"
